replies.body:
Why are you zeus? Origins of all your IGNs? I used to play God of War with my cousin a lot, the two main characters were Kratos, and Zeus. He liked Kratos, and I liked Zeus. zeus449 was a recommended  username, so I used it lol.Plys, the only reason I got Zeusy was because Zeus wasn't available ):
Is Dubai a great place??? -edit :)))) Big malls, cars, city life, hot weather, and sick hotels. YAAAS
Why did you come back from retirement? Will you even want to be admin again? I came back because I was bored xd, and no. Never going for admin again.
Why did you join Apollo? How was Insidia? I was very close to Apollo while I was in Insidia, because they were way more active than our team, and they let me chill in the channel with them. I joined, and loved it :P
Do you enjoy Pvp? Sword or bow? Sword, sword, sword, and sword. I'm a blind bat at bow.
Opinions on Avicus? How long do you think Avicus can survive for? As long as kylo isn't broke xd
Can I 1v1 you someday? I know I'll get thrashed but rip hit me up on Teamspeak anytime :p no you won't lol
Describe Posighdun. Zeus or Poseidon? :)))) Ugly name, looks ugly, god of the sea? ew
Opinions on me? Very nice guy, I remember you a long time ago, back when you rushed with no armor and helped me farm kills :P You are chill, I wish you spoke more often though, it's cool being around you. Plus, you improved a lot compared to the old days.
